sql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM stocks
WHERE stock_id NOT IN (
    SELECT stock_id
    FROM stock_sector
);

external_knowledge:
- "Pioneers in the stock market" refers to stocks with the earliest price matches before January 1, 1990; 
- "Made their debut" refers to the initial public offering (IPO) date; 
- "Dawn of a new decade" refers to January 1, 1990.
